When I run the second query on SQL Server 2008, I get an error. I had to change it to:&lt;br /&gt;
SELECT  schema_name = SCHEMA_NAME(schema_id) ,&lt;br /&gt;
        table_name = name&lt;br /&gt;
FROM    sys.tables&lt;br /&gt;
WHERE   OBJECTPROPERTY(OBJECT_ID, &#039;TableHasPrimaryKey&#039;) = 0&lt;br /&gt;
ORDER BY SCHEMA_NAME(schema_id) ,&lt;br /&gt;
        name;
